HENRY, Well, I didn't mean
any of those things I said.

40:54.952 --> 40:56.579
Yeah, you did.

40:56.662 --> 40:58.205
HENRY,
So, I ran all the way here

40:58.289 --> 40:59.874
to tell you that,
but then, uh...

41:01.458 --> 41:03.711
being stupid, I just stood
outside and watched you

41:03.794 --> 41:05.588
at the window
for about ten minutes.

41:05.671 --> 41:08.716
Ten minutes?
I only just sat down.

41:16.015 --> 41:17.016
Hi.

41:24.190 --> 41:26.859
How are
those French verbs coming?

41:30.446 --> 41:33.157
-I've missed you.
-Well, you just slept with me.

41:33.240 --> 41:37.745
-No. No, I didn't.
-Hey, come on.

41:37.828 --> 41:39.580
You just got yourself
a new young man.

41:39.663 --> 41:41.207
What kind of guy
do you think I am?

41:41.290 --> 41:42.875
As it turns out, an asshole.

41:44.376 --> 41:46.086
Was that the big secret,
you were keeping from me

41:46.170 --> 41:49.089
all these years?
You're a secret asshole?

41:49.840 --> 41:51.175
It's kind of every man's secret.

41:55.012 --> 41:56.680
-Was that me?
-Oh.

41:57.806 --> 42:00.893
Yeah. The first time
you threw a shoe at me.

42:02.853 --> 42:05.105
CLARE, I'm still not sorry.

42:05.189 --> 42:08.400
I grew up waiting for you.
Longing for you.

42:08.484 --> 42:10.152
-I know.
-No, you don't.

42:12.321 --> 42:16.575
I formed myself around you.
The idea of you.

42:18.077 --> 42:19.912
And you're an asshole.

42:22.790 --> 42:24.917
-Well here's the thing.

42:25.751 --> 42:27.920
The man you formed
yourself around,

42:28.003 --> 42:30.756
shock twist,
formed himself around you.

42:30.839 --> 42:32.800
-That's fucked up.
-Yep. So fucked up,

42:32.883 --> 42:35.135
it has a name. Marriage.

42:37.346 --> 42:39.390
Two people trying to be
the person the other one

42:39.473 --> 42:41.767
already thinks they are.
Love, basically.

42:41.850 --> 42:43.227
You didn't hear
what he just said.

42:43.310 --> 42:47.439
Clare, I said what he just said.
You wanna know why I said it?

42:47.523 --> 42:50.734
Because time travel is awful.
It is shit scary.

42:50.818 --> 42:52.611
It is waiting for the next storm
to hit.

42:52.695 --> 42:54.321
Wondering if this time
it's gonna kill you.

42:54.405 --> 42:57.116
That boy out there.
Time travel has never

42:57.199 --> 42:58.826
done one nice thing for him.

43:00.869 --> 43:02.329
Until today.

43:02.413 --> 43:04.915
Today he gets the winning
lottery ticket.

43:04.999 --> 43:07.501
-So, why is he being such--
-You know, what's even worse,

43:07.585 --> 43:09.461
than being terrified
all the time?

43:10.462 --> 43:11.505
The future.

43:12.589 --> 43:14.258
The future is the scariest thing
in the world.

43:14.341 --> 43:16.093
Because suddenly,
you are all in.

43:17.303 --> 43:20.180
-No choice.

43:20.264 --> 43:23.517
Anyone can stand any kind
of torture, except hope.

43:23.600 --> 43:25.060
Why didn't he just say all that?

43:27.146 --> 43:28.188
He did.

43:29.356 --> 43:31.483
It just took me a while.

43:40.200 --> 43:42.870
-That's a shit jacket.

43:43.245 --> 43:44.330
Well...

43:44.413 --> 43:49.877
Muggers can't be choosers.

43:49.960 --> 43:51.879
And now you're off home.

43:51.962 --> 43:55.382
In a minute, yeah.

43:55.466 --> 43:58.719
-To older me?
-To my wife.

43:58.802 --> 44:00.804
-Bitch.
-HENRY, Sorry?

44:00.888 --> 44:03.807
Older me gets you.
And I get younger you,

44:03.891 --> 44:05.017
who's a dick. It's not fair.

44:05.100 --> 44:07.561
No, he's not a dick.
And you know that.

44:07.644 --> 44:08.687
He's not you.

44:10.856 --> 44:13.317
Seriously,
how does he get to be you?

44:14.109 --> 44:15.527
What happens to him? Does he--

44:15.611 --> 44:17.237
Does he get hit
by a fucking meteorite?

44:17.321 --> 44:19.073
Yeah, going by the name
of Clare.

44:22.534 --> 44:23.702
That a compliment?

44:23.786 --> 44:25.829
I just called you a meteorite.
Take it any way you like.

44:28.207 --> 44:32.252
Hey. Look on the bright side.
He is way hotter than me.

44:33.337 --> 44:35.047
-No, he's not.
-Sure, he is.

44:41.512 --> 44:44.723
It's okay. I don't mind.
In fact, I agree with you.

44:44.807 --> 44:45.933
I've fucked him, too.

44:49.812 --> 44:51.438
I'll have a whiskey and soda.

45:01.073 --> 45:02.533
-Henry.
-Henry.

45:03.242 --> 45:04.910
-How's Ingrid?
-Good.

45:04.993 --> 45:07.746
Might go see her tonight, since
this isn't working out.

45:07.830 --> 45:09.665
I thought it was working out
pretty well already.

45:09.748 --> 45:11.291
Mind your own business.

45:11.834 --> 45:13.544
Hey!

45:13.627 --> 45:15.504
-Not that I'd ever offer advice.
-God forbid.

45:15.587 --> 45:17.339
HENRY, But a boring old man
told me something

45:17.423 --> 45:18.757
a very long time ago.

45:18.841 --> 45:20.759
He said you have two things to
do with your time on this Earth.

45:20.843 --> 45:24.138
One, find the love of your life.
Two, die as slowly as possible.

45:24.221 --> 45:26.640
You did part one tonight.
Part two starts now.

45:26.723 --> 45:28.600
Play time is over.

45:28.684 --> 45:30.477
Do you ever get bored
of hearing yourself talk?

45:30.561 --> 45:32.396
I don't know.
You tell me.

45:33.188 --> 45:35.524
No more time to waste, junior.

45:35.607 --> 45:37.526
You've seen the blood,
you know something's coming.

45:38.610 --> 45:40.654
-Yeah. But not today.

45:40.737 --> 45:43.449
Oh. Time for you
to fuck off then.

45:43.532 --> 45:45.033
-Get a haircut.

46:40.297 --> 46:42.591
-When were you?

46:49.556 --> 46:51.433
-Oh.

46:52.309 --> 46:54.228
I'm sorry
I threw my shoe at you.

46:57.856 --> 46:59.858
-Well, it's about time.
-Hmm.

47:37.729 --> 47:38.730
Hello.

47:40.148 --> 47:41.149
Henry?

48:02.212 --> 48:04.423
CLARE, Long ago,
men went to sea

48:04.506 --> 48:06.633
and women waited for them.

48:06.717 --> 48:08.677
Standing on the edge
of the water,

48:08.760 --> 48:11.179
scanning the horizon
for the tiny ship.

48:13.932 --> 48:17.185
Now, I wait for Henry.

48:21.189 --> 48:24.943
Not today.
Not today.

48:26.862 --> 48:29.281
I hate to be where she is not.

48:29.364 --> 48:32.326
And yet I'm always going
and she can't follow.

48:35.037 --> 48:37.706
Why does he always go
where I cannot follow?
